data.description: Welcome to your own piece of island living on Pine Island, Florida! This 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom split level single-family home offers the perfect blend of island living and a chill vibe. Nestled on a sprawling 2.65-acre lot, this idyllic retreat is just waiting for you to call it home. As you approach the property, you'll immediately notice the abundance of lush greenery and the tranquil private fresh fish stocked pond a true oasis from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Zoned AG2, the property offers a myriad of possibilities for gardening, small hobby farming, or simply enjoying the great outdoors. Spacious floor plan featuring a mix of plush carpeting and elegant hardwood floors. The stunning cathedral ceilings provide an airy, open feel throughout the home! Outside, you'll find ample parking with space for two vehicles inside the garage as well as plenty of outdoor parking of boats, trailers, and RV’s outside. Room to add a pool, a workshop, or any other outdoor amenities your heart desires. The Chicken Coop, Pig Pasture, Dog Run and outbuildings convey. Come experience all the charm and beauty this NON-HURRICANE IAN DAMAGED OR FLOODED home has to offer.
